snippet.title: Walkabout Mini Golf - Official Meow Wolf Course Reveal Trailer | Upload VR Showcase Winter 2023
snippet.description: Walkabout Mini Golf is a VR mini golf game developed by Mighty Coconut. Take a look at the reveal of the latest course coming to the game titled Numina, made in collaboration with Mighty Coconut and Meow Wolf. The course inspired by the real world location at Meow Wolf's office and emphasizes the vibrant colors and design of the course for players to enjoy. The Numina course for Walkabout Mini Golf is releasing on December 7.
